latestIgtvVideos.caption:

#valentinesdance #lovefordance 

You may celebrate any kind of love on a Valentine's Day.. it's just not meant for lovers. For me there is no greater joy than dancing my heart out to music hence I dedicate this beautiful day to celebrate what I love .. DANCE. 
Thanks @amitshaw_dna  for tirelessly being there for me in everything I do. It's only you who can do magic in directing whatever I conceptualize.

Thank you @arun.dancerdude88
for giving all the time and dedication for rehearsals despite of your ill health. 
Thanks Ipshita for being there. 
Thank you Universe for always guiding me. 

Wishing all of you a HAPPY VALENTINE'S DAY. LOVE N CELEBRATE.

latestIgtvVideos.title: LIGGI  DANCE COVER  CHILLED CHOREO
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Last one week was just full of pain and turmoil..
After the  doctor's green card for dance yesterday i was happy but the silly antibiotics had a another plan ..
After going to Studio i felt like a bored buffalo with a swelled up abdomen trying to do some admin work..
Screw that.. got up took a class and tried a chilled dance cover to uplift that mood back.
Here i am.. Happy and full of spirits again. 😀😀😀

P.s. This choreography is done keeping those wretched antibiotics repurcussions in mind hence movement is limited.😉😉😂😂🙄🙄

#dancedatewithdna
When @nupur.laddha thought about how she wanted to celebrate her birthday this year, she decided to skip the usual dinners and parties. Instead, she chose something deeply personal and joyful—a dance date with Pulkit at DNA.. For Nupur, dance has always been more than movement; it's a way of expressing her soul, and sharing that with Pulkit made it even more special.

As they stepped onto the studio floor, laughter and music filled the air. From playful spins to soulful lifts, their chemistry was undeniable. Every beat brought them closer, every rhythm unfolded new emotions. They danced through joy, love, and even a little nostalgia—remembering how far they'd come together.

The session wasn’t just about technique; it was about connection. Pulkit matched Nupur’s energy with ease, letting the music guide their flow. 
By the end, both were glowing—super happy anf feeling successful in dancing from the heart. For Nupur, it was the perfect birthday: not just a celebration of another year, but of love, movement, and togetherness. And for both, a dance date to remember.
#dancewithdorothy #dorothymajumdar #dancedatewithdna #giftideas #birthday #anniversary
